get.description:
Pre-rendered HTML for /bot/{agent_id}.

- Crawler UA  → full HTML with meta tags + JSON-LD (200 text/html)
- Browser UA  → JSON with redirect URL (200 application/json)

Production nginx snippet (add alongside /m/ in nginx-og-routes.conf):
  location /bot/ {
    if ($http_user_agent ~* "googlebot|twitterbot|linkedinbot|facebot|...") {
      proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:8001;
      rewrite ^/bot/(.*)$ /api/ssr/bot/$1 break;
    }
    proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:3000;
  }

